products.title: HP Pavilion Gaming Laptop Ryzen 5600h 8gb RAM
products.desc: Processor: AMD Ryzen 5 5600H (up to 4.2 GHz max boost clock(2i), 16 MB L3 cache, 6 cores, 12 thread) (2.1 GHz base clock speed, up to 3.7 GHz max boost clock, 4 MB L3 cache, 4 cores). Memory: 8 GB DDR4-3200 (1 x 8 GB), Up to 16 GB DDR4-3200 SDRAM. Storage: 512 GB PCIe NVMe M.2 SSD. Display: 39.6 cm (15.6 inch) diagonal, FHD (1920 x 1080), IPS, micro-edge, anti-glare, 250 nits, 45% NTSC, 60Hz refresh rate display screen
